Project context:
  Algorithm: SUMMA parallel matrix multiplication.
  Parallelism level: data parallelism.
  Decomposition: two-dimensional block data decomposition.
  Mapping: q x q process grid; each rank owns an N/q x N/q block.
  Communication: blocking MPI point-to-point for scatter/gather and MPI_Bcast for SUMMA panels.
  Topology: logical 2D Cartesian grid with row and column communicators.
  Load balance: equal-size matrix blocks when N is divisible by q.

